**/*_rsa*
**/*_dsa*
**/*_ecdsa*
**/*_ed25519*
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.key
**/*.crt
**/*.cert
**/*.cer

# GPG/PGP Keys
**/*.gpg
**/*.asc
**/*.pgp
private_**/gnupg/
private_**/gpg/

# API Keys and Tokens
**/*token*
**/*secret*
**/*password*
**/*credential*
**/.env
**/api_key*
**/auth_token*

# Password Manager Data
**/*.kdbx
**/*.1pif
**/Passwords.txt

